The number of confirmed COVID-19 cases in England so far as at 20 November is 1,267,276 (2,251.5 cases per 100,000 population). In the seven days to 15 November, there were 149,898 new confirmed cases (266.3 new cases per 100,000). In the seven days to 08 November, there were 147,089 new cases and so the new cases have risen by 2% ( 2,809 extra cases).
